    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The HeadScript helper uses single line comments for CDATA:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$escapeStart = ($useCdata) ? '//' : '//&lt;!--';
$escapeEnd   = ($useCdata) ? '//'       : '//--&gt;';
</code></pre>

<p>I propose these should be changed to multi line comments as this will not break JavaScript when stripping newlines from html output.</p>

